OL,3,COver 100 media personalities sign open
OL,4,Cletter in support of Sangita Myska
OL,6,FMore than 100 media personalities,
OL,7,Factivists, broadcasters and lawyers
OL,8,Fhave signed a letter in support of
OL,9,Fjournalist Sangita Myska expressing
OL,10,F"deep concern at her sudden
OL,11,Fdisappearance from LBC", which was
OL,12,Ffour weeks ago this weekend.
OL,14,FThis letter - which has been written
OL,15,Findependently of - goes on to say her
OL,16,Fabsence has "shocked and upset her
OL,17,Fpeers and thousands of listeners
OL,18,Facross the UK".
