OL,3,COver 100 media personalities sign open
OL,4,Cletter in support of Sangita Myska
OL,6,FSignatories of the letter include ITV
OL,7,FNews' James Mates, musician Charlotte
OL,8,FChurch and MP for Coventry South,
OL,9,FZarah Sultana.
OL,11,FMs Myska, who hosts from 1pm to 4pm on
OL,12,FSaturdays and Sundays after joining in
OL,13,F2022, has not been broadcasting at the
OL,14,Fstation since reportedly being taken
OL,15,Foff air from April 20.
OL,17,FOn May 1, LBC confirmed the presenter
OL,18,Fwill leave at the end of her contract
OL,19,Fafter nearly two years.
