OL,3,COver 100 media personalities sign open
OL,4,Cletter in support of Sangita Myska
OL,6,FThe letter penned by her "colleagues,
OL,7,Ffriends, supporters and allies" wrote
OL,8,Fto express their "deep concern at her
OL,9,Fsudden disappearance from LBC".
OL,11,FIt reads: "Sangita's journalistic
OL,12,Frecord and professional integrity
OL,13,Fremains unimpeachable. HerJapproach is
OL,14,Ffair and balanced. She established a
OL,15,F'rare rapport' with her audience,
OL,16,Fauthor TimJWalker notes, at a time
OL,17,Fwhen public trust in the mainstream
OL,18,Fmedia is low. Our concern isJrecent
OL,19,Fevents could undermine that trust
OL,20,Ffurther."
