OL,3,COver 100 media personalities sign open
OL,4,Cletter in support of Sangita Myska
OL,6,FHer absence from the airwaves led to
OL,7,Fan outpouring of support and questions
OL,8,Ffrom listeners and media outlets, with
OL,9,Fmore than 35,000 people so far signing
OL,10,Fa petition calling for LBC to
OL,11,Freinstate her.
OL,13,FUproar even trickled into last week's
OL,14,Flocal elections when London Mayoral
OL,15,Findependent candidate, Count Binface,
OL,16,Fanswered an LBC reporter "Where is
OL,17,FSangita Myska?" when he questioned
OL,18,FBinface on his loss.
