OL,6,FTom Cheal, LBC's senior managing
OL,7,Feditor, said: "We'd like to thank
OL,8,FSangita for her fantastic contribution
OL,9,Fto LBC and we wish her every success
OL,10,Fin the future."
OL,12,FFormer Conservative Party
OL,13,Fparliamentary candidate Ali Miraj has
OL,14,Fbeen stepping in as a guest presenter
OL,15,Fand he will now take over the weekend
OL,16,Fslot.JLBC also announced that Vanessa
OL,17,FFeltz will join the radio station in
OL,18,FMay following her departure from
OL,19,FTalkTV after the TV station moved to
OL,20,Fbroadcasting via streamers including
OL,21,FYouTube.
